Freddie dashboard agents section design decision (deferred): agent xstate machine state is NOT exposed via HTTP API. To add an agents view requires: (1) export agent machine snapshot from src/agent/machine.js, (2) add /api/agents endpoint returning {count, active, metrics, session_associations}, (3) add #/agents route + PAGES entry in src/web/app.js (and now in anentrypoint-design since all GUI moves there), (4) register window.__debug.agents() observability global. Open design questions: which metrics (count? perf data? session associations?); whether to push via SSE or poll; whether to surface tool-call timeline per agent.